		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />On top of my head a romhacker might want to type over raw nametable data (most often static graphics like a title screen or menu). First in RAM to get instant feedback on the edits, then copy (or translate, if it is derived from structures or RLE) the result to ROM to save it.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
