	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It was pretty trivial to implement (4 whole lines of code), so I give it a shot.  Build: <a href="https://www.mesen.ca/MesenMar26.zip" class="postlink">download</a><br /><br />Basically, hold Alt and put your mouse over any byte you want to change, scroll up to increment by 1, down to decrement by 1.<br />I can't really see myself using this in most scenarios, but considering it's 4 lines of code, I don't mind keeping it in if it's useful to someone :p

		

